.env
.env.*
# Re-allow committed example/template env files. The
# `*.env.example` pattern covers `deploy/.env.compose.example` and
# any future `.env.<role>.example` files; the bare `.env.example`
# entry covers a top-level template.
!.env.example
!*.env.example
!.env.*.example